examples.en: Dolphins produce a high frequency sound.
Dolphins show a high level of intelligence.
Dolphins were talking their own dolphin talk.
Do dolphins possess the ability to use language?
Dolphins sometimes play in the wake of the boats.
She described watching dolphins play beside the ship.
We stood on the deck and watched dolphins swim near the ship.
The study disproves any notion that dolphins are not intelligent.
Scientists studied the reproduction, diet, and health of the dolphins.
The scheme to save the stranded dolphins miscarried, and all were lost.
There are several accounts of dolphins living in close proximity to humans (=close to humans).
